==地名起源<ref name="大甲道卡斯">{{Cite book| author =李安娜等| title =《大甲道卡斯 : 鐵砧山風景特定區導覽》| location =臺灣臺中| publisher =臺中縣大甲鎮公所| date =2004-03-23| pages =11| ISBN =| accessdate =2016-10-02| url =http://old.dajia.taichung.gov.tw/book10/EB00K11-A02.htm#1| language =zh-tw| quote =| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20160824002933/http://old.dajia.taichung.gov.tw/book10/EB00K11-A02.htm#1| archivedate =2016-08-24}}</ref>==
關於大甲之名的起源，存在兩種說法：
*[[河洛話|河洛話]]的大甲類似道卡斯(TAOKAS)的譯音，源於當時外來的漢人對以當地[[道卡斯族|道卡斯族]]稱呼此地地名，而由此推斷部分學者認為大甲為[[道卡斯族|道卡斯族]]的大本營。
*源於易經拆字學所帶來的不同說法，「大」- 「大字頭出天，兩腳八字開」；「甲」- 「甲字成田，帶有尾」。

==行政區劃變更<ref>{{Cite book| author =陳明終等| title =《大甲風貌》| location =臺灣臺中| publisher =鐵砧山青年社| date =1981-08| pages =1687-1770| ISBN =| accessdate =2016-10-02| url =http://old.dajia.taichung.gov.tw/book14/the-history/1687-1770.pdf| language =zh-tw| quote =| deadurl =yes| archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20150403204539/http://old.dajia.taichung.gov.tw/book14/the-history/1687-1770.pdf| archivedate =2015-04-03}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www1.geo.ntnu.edu.tw/webs/teacher/Yan-Zhao%20Wei/course/life_geography/life_geo/chp8_history%20geography.pdf |title = 地理實察課程資料 第八章、臺灣之歷史地理概論 |author = 韋煙灶 |date =  |publisher =  |language = zh-tw |accessdate = 2016-10-02 |quote =  |archive-date = 2016-10-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20161002194156/http://www1.geo.ntnu.edu.tw/webs/teacher/Yan-Zhao%20Wei/course/life_geography/life_geo/chp8_history%20geography.pdf |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.moi.gov.tw/dca/02place_002_06.aspx |title = 地方行政區域簡介 |author = 內政部民政司 |date =  |publisher = 內政部民政司 |language = zh-tw |accessdate = 2016-10-02 |quote =  |archive-date = 2017-02-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170202012936/http://www.moi.gov.tw/DCA/02place_002_06.aspx |dead-url = yes }}</ref>==
